\c 15
\s Mirairo yezvipiriso
\p
\v 1 Zvino Jehovha wakataura kuna Mozisi achiti:
\v 2 Taura kuvana vaIsraeri ugoti kwavari: Pamunosvika munyika yeugaro hwenyu, yandinopa kwamuri;
\v 3 muchiita chipo chemoto kuna Jehovha, kana chibairo chekuzadzisa mhiko, kana chipo chekuzvidira kana mitambo yenyu yakamiswa, kuita hwema hunonhuhwira kuna Jehovha, zvinobva pamombe kana pamakwai;
\v 4 zvino iye anopa chipo chake kuna Jehovha ngaauye nechipo chechidyiwa chechegumi cheefa yeupfu hwakakanyiwa nechechina chehini yemafuta;
\v 5 nechechina chehini yewaini yechipo chechinwiwa, achazvigadzira nechipo chinopiswa kana chibairo, chegwai rimwe.
\v 6 Kana chegondobwe, uchagadzira kuva chipo chechidyiwa, zvegumi zviviri zveupfu hwakakanyiwa nechetatu chehini yemafuta;
\v 7 nechechipo chechinwiwa, uchapa chetatu chehini yewaini, zvive hwema hunonhuhwira kuna Jehovha.
\v 8 Zvino kana uchigadzira nzombe diki kuva chipo chinopiswa, kana chibairo chekuzadzisa mhiko, kana zvipo zvekuyananisa kuna Jehovha;
\v 9 zvino achapa nzombe diki mhuru yemombe chive chipo chechidyiwa chezvegumi zvitatu zveupfu hwakakanyiwa nehafu yehini yemafuta.
\v 10 Zvino iwe uchauisa hafu hehini yewaini yechipo chechinwiwa, chipo chemoto, chehwema hunonhuhwira kuna Jehovha.
\v 11 Zvichaitwa saizvozvo panzombe iyi, kana pagondobwe iri, kana pagwayana iri, kana pambudzana iyi.
\v 12 Zvichienderana neuwandu hwauchagadzira. uchaita saizvozvo kune kune chimwe nechimwe zvichienderana neuwandu hwacho.
\v 13 Vese vanoberekerwa munyika vachaita zvinhu izvi nemutoo uyu, pakupa chipo chemoto, chehwema hunonhuhwira kuna Jehovha.
\v 14 Zvino kana mweni ari mutorwa pakati penyu, kana ani nani pakati penyu kusvika kumazera enyu achida kupa chipo chemoto chehwema hunonhuhwira kuna Jehovha, sezvamunoita, achaita.
\v 15 Paungano yenyu panofanira kuva nomutemo umwe wenyu nowomutorwa agere nemi, uve murairo usingaperi, kusvikira kumazera enyu; sezvamakaita imwi, ndizvo zvinofanira kuita mutorwa pamberi paJehovha.
\v 16 Munofanira kuva nomurairo umwe netsika imwe, imwi nomutorwa agere nemi.
\p
\v 17 Jehovha akataura naMozisi, akati:
\v 18 Taura navana vaIsraeri uti kwavari: Kana muchisvika kunyika kwandinokuisai,
\v 19 kana modya zvokudya zvenyika, munofanira kupa Jehovha chipo.
\v 20 Pazvitsva zvoupfu hwenyu munofanira kuuya nechingwa chive chipo; sezvamunoita nechipo cheburiro, munofanira kuchitsaura saizvozvo.
\v 21 Munofanira kupa Jehovha pazvitsva zvoupfu hwenyu chipo kusvikira kumazera enyu.
\p
\v 22 Kana muchitadza, musingachengeti mirairo iyi yese, yakataurwa naJehovha kuna Mozisi,
\v 23 zvese zvamakarairwa naJehovha nomuromo waMozisi, kubva pazuva rakatanga kuraira Jehovha, kusvikira kumazera enyu,
\v 24 zvino kana zvichinge zvaitwa ungano isingazivi, ungano yese inofanira kuuya nenzombe imwe diki, chive chipo chinopiswa, chive chinonhuhwira zvakanaka kuna Jehovha, pamwe chete nechipo chacho choupfu, nechipo chacho chinodururwa, sezvakarairwa, nenhongo imwe yembudzi, chive chipo chezvivi.
\v 25 Mupristi anofanira kuitira ungano yese yavana vaIsraeri chiyananiso, vakanganwirwe; nokuti kwaiva kutadza, vakazouya nechipo chavo pamberi paJehovha, chiri chipo chemoto kuna Jehovha, nechipo chezvivi pamusoro pokutadza kwavo.
\v 26 Ipapo ungano yese yavana vaIsraeri ichakanganwirwa, nomutorwa agere pakati pavo; nokuti vanhu vese vakange vazviita havo nokusaziva.
\p
\v 27 Kana munhu umwe akatadza nokusaziva, anofanira kuuya nesheche yembudzi yegore rimwe, chive chipo chezvivi.
\v 28 Zvino mupristi anofanira kuitira munhu chiyananiso, akatadza, kana akaita zvivi nokusaziva, pamberi paJehovha, kuti amuyananisire, akanganwirwe.
\v 29 Munofanira kuva nomurairo mumwechete pamusoro pomunhu akaita chinhu nokusaziva, kana ari munhu akaberekerwa panyika pakati pavana vaIsraeri, kana ari mutorwa agere pakati pavo.
\p
\v 30 Asi munhu anoita chinhu nokuzvikudza, kana ari munhu akaberekerwa munyika, kana ari mutorwa, iye anomhura Jehovha; munhu uyo anofanira kugurwa kubva pavanhu vekwake.
\v 31 Nokuti akazvidza shoko raJehovha, akaputsa murairo wake; munhu uyu anofanira kubviswa chose; mhosva yokutadza kwake iri pamusoro pake. Munhu akadarika murairo wesabata anourawa.
\p
\v 32 Zvino vana vaIsraeri vachiri murenje, vakaona munhu achiunganidza tsotso nomusi wesabata.
\v 33 Avo vakamuwana achiunganidza tsotso vakamuisa kuna Mozisi naAroni, nokuungano yese.
\v 34 Vakamuisa mutirongo, nokuti kwakange kusina kurehwa zvaaifanira kuitirwa.
\v 35 Jehovha akati kuna Mozisi: Munhu uyu, zvirokwazvo, anofanira kuurawa; ungano yese inofanira kumutaka namabwe kunze kwemisasa.
\v 36 Ipapo ungano yese yakamuisa kunze kwemisasa, vakamutaka namabwe, akafa; sezvakange zvarairwa Mozisi naJehovha.
\s Chiratidzo chinofanira kuiswa panguvo dzavo
\p
\v 37 Zvino Jehovha akataura naMozisi, akati:
\v 38 Taura navana vaIsraeri, uvaraire kuti vazviitire masa pamipendero yenguvo dzavo, kusvikira kumarudzi avo ese, vaise paisa rimwe nerimwe pamupendero rwonzi rutema.
\v 39 Chinofanira kuva kwamuri isa ramungasiona, mugorangarira mirairo yese yaJehovha, kuti muiite; kuti murege kutevera kuda komoyo yenyu nokwameso enyu, kwamaisitevera pakupata kwenyu;
\v 40 kuti murangarire nokuita mirairo yangu yese, nokuva vatsvene kuna Mwari wenyu.
\v 41 Ndini Jehovha wenyu, akakubudisai munyika yeEgipita, kuti ndive Mwari wenyu; ndini Jehovha Mwari wenyu.
